1
00:00:38,820 --> 00:00:40,820
=Visage and Soul=

2
00:00:40,820 --> 00:00:43,040
("The Unique Her"
Trilogy on Women's Relationships)

3
00:00:44,720 --> 00:00:47,640
=Episode 13=

4
00:00:54,120 --> 00:00:56,720
Don't tell me you've
actually fallen for Qiao Xiaomi.

5
00:01:07,105 --> 00:01:10,638
♪Dawn and night♪

6
00:01:10,665 --> 00:01:13,298
♪Poems and moonlight♪

7
00:01:13,657 --> 00:01:15,983
♪Whether my heart beats or not♪

8
00:01:16,320 --> 00:01:17,400
Xiaomi?

9
00:01:18,880 --> 00:01:20,280
Where did you go?

10
00:01:20,280 --> 00:01:21,806
♪I don't want it♪

11
00:01:21,819 --> 00:01:24,026
♪Roses are far too showy♪

12
00:01:24,582 --> 00:01:26,862
♪I gaze across the shimmering lake♪

13
00:01:27,320 --> 00:01:34,320
♪Touch down♪

14
00:01:34,330 --> 00:01:41,320
♪Touch down♪

15
00:01:41,330 --> 00:01:46,280
♪Touch down♪

16
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:47,960
Why are you back so late?

17
00:01:48,320 --> 00:01:55,320
♪Touch down♪

18
00:01:56,600 --> 00:01:58,080
Were you out doing something bad?

19
00:01:58,280 --> 00:02:05,280
♪Touch down♪

20
00:02:05,290 --> 00:02:12,280
♪Touch down♪

21
00:02:12,290 --> 00:02:14,920
♪Touch down♪

22
00:02:15,081 --> 00:02:17,814
♪Dawn and night♪

23
00:02:18,106 --> 00:02:20,533
♪Poems and moonlight♪

24
00:02:20,937 --> 00:02:23,410
♪Whether my heart beats or not♪

25
00:02:23,427 --> 00:02:26,526
♪Let her touch down♪

26
00:02:26,566 --> 00:02:29,000
♪I don't want it♪

27
00:02:29,030 --> 00:02:32,098
♪Roses are far too showy♪

28
00:02:32,138 --> 00:02:34,550
♪I gaze across the shimmering lake♪

29
00:02:34,590 --> 00:02:41,590
♪Touch down♪

30
00:03:04,200 --> 00:03:05,880
(What am I doing?)

31
00:03:51,112 --> 00:03:57,998
♪There's no point in keeping this up♪

32
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:01,720
(How could I)

33
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:03,040
(ever mistake her for you?)

34
00:04:03,040 --> 00:04:07,880
♪You might as well pack up and leave♪

35
00:04:09,764 --> 00:04:15,844
♪Being with you won't lead anywhere♪

36
00:04:18,453 --> 00:04:21,680
♪We've long been stuck
on each other♪

37
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:22,840
(Xiaoduo.)

38
00:04:25,226 --> 00:04:28,120
♪Why don't you understand?♪

39
00:04:28,165 --> 00:04:35,312
♪Go find your own simple happiness♪

40
00:04:36,130 --> 00:04:37,400
♪Don't come and destroy me♪

41
00:04:37,400 --> 00:04:38,480
(Sorry.)

42
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:39,360
(Xiaoduo.)

43
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:41,720
(Back in that fire,)

44
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:45,320
(I failed to save you. My fault.)

45
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:47,160
(And now,)

46
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:49,480
(I mistook her for you.)

47
00:04:50,080 --> 00:04:51,560
(That's my fault too.)

48
00:04:52,191 --> 00:04:57,611
♪Only seeing you fall♪

49
00:04:57,636 --> 00:05:01,643
♪Would make me truly happy♪

50
00:05:04,456 --> 00:05:10,536
♪Someday I'll come see
you with my luggage♪

51
00:05:10,588 --> 00:05:15,782
♪Watching you cry alone♪

52
00:05:15,793 --> 00:05:20,320
♪While I travel away with a smile♪

53
00:05:20,341 --> 00:05:24,294
♪Without a trace of emotion♪

54
00:05:32,200 --> 00:05:33,240
Qiao Xiaomi!

55
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:34,240
Do you really think

56
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:35,680
you can do whatever you want?

57
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:36,600
Get away from me!

58
00:05:38,640 --> 00:05:39,560
Xiaomi!

59
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:40,520
Calm down.

60
00:05:40,880 --> 00:05:42,120
Is anyone there?

61
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:43,400
Is anyone there...

62
00:05:43,680 --> 00:05:44,920
Help!

63
00:06:00,520 --> 00:06:01,440
Don't be afraid.

64
00:06:01,840 --> 00:06:02,840
Take my hand.

65
00:06:03,400 --> 00:06:04,920
I'll get you somewhere safe.

66
00:06:05,440 --> 00:06:06,360
Ye Xiaoduo.

67
00:06:07,280 --> 00:06:08,960
You're Ye Xiaoduo, right?

68
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:20,920
Ye Xiaoduo.

69
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:22,760
Ye Xiaoduo!

70
00:06:24,840 --> 00:06:25,720
Ye Xiaoduo.

71
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:27,440
Ye Xiaoduo!

72
00:06:33,960 --> 00:06:34,760
Ye Xiaoduo.

73
00:06:39,880 --> 00:06:40,920
Qin Yu.

74
00:06:43,320 --> 00:06:44,360
Qin Yu.

75
00:06:46,160 --> 00:06:47,160
Qin Yu!

76
00:06:57,040 --> 00:07:00,760
♪Happy birthday to you♪

77
00:07:01,400 --> 00:07:04,920
♪Happy birthday to you♪

78
00:07:06,280 --> 00:07:07,880
You're not about to cry, are you?

79
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:10,240
Anyone who tells me a story

80
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,480
gets free bread.

81
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:13,720
I want to live in the moment.

82
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:16,080
What took you so long to get back?

83
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:18,760
These past three years,

84
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:22,360
I've had such a hard time on my own.

85
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:27,480
If I still haven't seen Qiao Xiaomi

86
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:29,520
sign the stock transfer agreement,

87
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:31,960
don't blame me for turning against you.

88
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:40,080
Xiaomi.

89
00:07:40,400 --> 00:07:41,880
I know I made a huge mistake.

90
00:07:41,880 --> 00:07:44,000
But I honestly didn't
know it was a fake.

91
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:45,240
It was my negligence.

92
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:49,040
Please give me one more chance.

93
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:51,760
This job means everything to me.

94
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:55,120
Not calling the police was mercy enough.

95
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:56,720
Stop testing my limits.

96
00:07:56,720 --> 00:07:57,880
Xiaomi.

97
00:07:58,240 --> 00:08:00,120
Think about how well
I used to treat you.

98
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:02,440
Whenever you got in trouble,
who covered for you?

99
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:06,680
Please give me one more chance, okay?

100
00:08:08,840 --> 00:08:09,640
No.

101
00:08:11,280 --> 00:08:12,840
That's not how I do things.

102
00:08:14,640 --> 00:08:15,720
Qiao Xiaomi.

103
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:17,200
You never used to be like this.

104
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:19,160
I'm not who I used to be.

105
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:21,960
Get out of my office

106
00:08:21,960 --> 00:08:23,520
before I call security.

107
00:08:24,200 --> 00:08:25,120
Otherwise,

108
00:08:26,880 --> 00:08:29,320
I'll deal with your precious Zhiwei too.

109
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:37,160
Do you really think

110
00:08:37,160 --> 00:08:38,720
I'm doing this because of Zhiwei?

111
00:08:40,280 --> 00:08:41,760
No, because of Ye Xiaoduo.

112
00:08:42,360 --> 00:08:44,680
The person you hated most
used to be Ye Xiaoduo.

113
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:47,480
You weren't even fit
to stand beside her.

114
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:50,520
You were insanely jealous of her.

115
00:08:50,520 --> 00:08:51,200
So,

116
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:52,680
you deliberately set her up

117
00:08:52,680 --> 00:08:54,000
to be trapped in that fire.

118
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:54,520
Right?

119
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:57,280
What you didn't expect

120
00:08:58,160 --> 00:09:00,480
was that the fire would destroy you too.

121
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:06,720
Ye Xiaoduo was right.

122
00:09:06,920 --> 00:09:07,880
The strong

123
00:09:07,880 --> 00:09:09,680
never bully the weak,

124
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:12,120
because that's the most
cowardly thing of all.

125
00:09:26,849 --> 00:09:31,872
(Ye Xiaoduo. Fire. Jealousy.)

126
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:36,880
Say that again.

127
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:38,160
Got a problem with that?

128
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:40,680
I really don't get it.

129
00:09:40,680 --> 00:09:42,320
Why do girls like you,
illegitimate daughters,

130
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:43,800
always so defiant?

131
00:09:44,560 --> 00:09:45,800
Ye Xiaoduo was right.

132
00:09:46,040 --> 00:09:48,480
The strong never bully the weak,

133
00:09:48,880 --> 00:09:50,760
because that's the most
cowardly thing of all.

134
00:09:51,800 --> 00:09:53,400
Ye Xiaoduo already lost her mother.

135
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:55,600
Why did we still bully her?

136
00:09:55,600 --> 00:09:57,280
She's already dead.

137
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:59,440
Who are you saying all this for?

138
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:01,600
So,

139
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:03,440
I really was such a terrible person.

140
00:10:10,320 --> 00:10:11,520
Do you know Ye Xiaoduo?

141
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:13,520
She's your half-sister.

142
00:10:15,760 --> 00:10:17,560
Could it be that losing my memories

143
00:10:17,920 --> 00:10:18,920
was Heaven's way of giving me

144
00:10:18,920 --> 00:10:20,600
a second chance at life?

145
00:10:21,440 --> 00:10:22,480
Was I...

146
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:24,280
really that awful before?

147
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:26,800
You're the kindest,

148
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:28,000
sweetest girl

149
00:10:28,280 --> 00:10:29,400
I've ever met.

150
00:10:30,680 --> 00:10:31,920
I know what you're afraid of.

151
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:34,240
But I'm here for you.

152
00:10:35,480 --> 00:10:36,560
From now on,

153
00:10:37,280 --> 00:10:38,760
you don't have to fear anything.

154
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:41,000
(No.)

155
00:10:41,520 --> 00:10:42,880
(I have to find out the truth.)

156
00:10:43,280 --> 00:10:45,080
(If I really did something wrong,)

157
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:46,400
(then I have to face the consequences.)

158
00:10:48,880 --> 00:10:50,480
The number you dialed is busy.

159
00:10:50,800 --> 00:10:52,640
Please try again later.

160
00:10:55,400 --> 00:10:56,320
(Could it be)

161
00:10:56,640 --> 00:10:58,640
(does he regret what happened
last night?)

162
00:10:59,680 --> 00:11:01,280
(When he left me back then,)

163
00:11:01,280 --> 00:11:03,000
(did he think I was that awful too?)

164
00:11:03,640 --> 00:11:04,480
(No.)

165
00:11:05,240 --> 00:11:06,760
(I need to ask him myself.)

166
00:11:11,600 --> 00:11:13,280
Qin Yu, why won't you answer your phone?

167
00:11:17,040 --> 00:11:17,640
Qin...

168
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:27,400
Qin Yu.

169
00:11:29,040 --> 00:11:29,800
Qin Yu.

170
00:11:32,200 --> 00:11:33,800
Let me take you to the hospital, Qin Yu.

171
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:35,280
No.

172
00:11:36,160 --> 00:11:36,960
Medicine.

173
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:39,200
Medicine.

174
00:12:20,108 --> 00:12:22,178
♪We say good morning, we say good night♪

175
00:12:22,178 --> 00:12:25,598
♪We say we miss each other,
but never speak of the hurt♪

176
00:12:27,198 --> 00:12:29,088
♪The sweeter it is, the luckier we seem♪

177
00:12:29,088 --> 00:12:33,078
♪Yet the more romantic,
the rougher the road♪

178
00:12:34,318 --> 00:12:36,178
♪Let me go, set me free♪

179
00:12:36,178 --> 00:12:40,218
♪Let me drown in reckless silence♪

180
00:12:40,758 --> 00:12:46,168
♪We were perfect for each other,
yet you never admitted it♪

181
00:12:47,518 --> 00:12:49,658
♪The freedom you gave me♪

182
00:12:49,658 --> 00:12:53,298
♪Became the heaviest chain I bear♪

183
00:12:54,558 --> 00:12:56,828
♪Love can barely move forward♪

184
00:12:56,828 --> 00:13:00,608
♪Yet the words still linger unspoken♪

185
00:13:01,708 --> 00:13:03,948
♪The closeness I long for♪

186
00:13:03,948 --> 00:13:08,338
♪There's no need for you
to keep avoiding it♪

187
00:13:08,748 --> 00:13:10,568
♪I don't want to break free♪

188
00:13:10,568 --> 00:13:15,938
♪Take back the chains
disguised as freedom♪
